！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>廢話唔多講！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>水魔法<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4</span></span>大好處</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1.遠程攻擊</strong></span><br />\n玩過咁撚多次都知啦 近戰有幾吃裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n魔法師輕裝就玩得 門檻低又安全<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>2.擾亂敵人</strong></span><br />\n水魔法最強大嘅係可以封閉D怪嘅視野 直接落Debuff攻擊力減50%<br />\n保障近戰勇士安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>3.高機動性</strong></span><br />\n玩Hit and Run 瘋狂拉打班近攻狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>4.低殺傷力</strong></span><br />\n跟本就係和理非天職 贏盡輿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">水魔法練成</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cX4x7VP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcX4x7VP.jpg&h=7b041680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.水氣球</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b3V5Jyo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb3V5Jyo.jpg&h=d49636ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2.水性乳膠漆</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J1Lxozi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ1Lxozi.png&h=9a0f41e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住係水性啊！！</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">TK咗都可以用水洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3.茄汁樽</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LheREiJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLheREiJ.jpg&h=ca2f81f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4.練成！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Jl4FPk_-hk8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJl4FPk_-hk8&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdRw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=703dab9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Jl4FPk_-hk8</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">效果圖</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6S1MtcS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6S1MtcS.jpg&h=615fa240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">水魔法師嘅加入將會大大增加各位玩家嘅遠距離作戰能力</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝各位玩家武運亨通 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Be Water Magician</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777386a2011b506aa6c9cac23fb60d64b96fdfeb","tid":1607795,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:16:22.000Z","msg":"Telegram 預設訊息可以保護到手足性命<br />\n希望大家可以幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火 TG: @Abccbbc<br />\n612 TG: @ReliefFund612<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"126b38cad67e82975b7e15369b27b83af7b0bc63","tid":1607795,"uid":65072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:19:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1435323/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1435323/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n點解唔開發新技能用水，對popo傷害好大<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n見上一個po咁多人支持， 睇完下面啲留言，做啲歸納先<br />\n1）加咩都得， 大家創意無限我喺度講都講唔曬<br />\n2）可樂加萬樂珠<br />\n3）可攻擊(濕，笠，臭)，可防禦(跌)<br />\n4）濕膠袋自帶跣既效果<br />\n5）水攻係辛苦死佢地，無孔不入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解決技術性問題<br />\n1）射程: 我哋依家有大彈弓, 但係其實就算掉得唔遠都唔怕, <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>佢地前面成地都係不明液體包括油，梘同埋爆咗嘅膠袋, 跣都跣死</strong></span>，最梗要夠多<br />\n<br />\n2）水:依家打地區戰，水喉水供應多咗， 不過都會有運上前線嘅問題， <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>可能要用黃白藍膠袋或者街市車嗰啲先運到大量， 但係回歸返原始方法， 用人鏈逐隻逐隻保鮮袋水彈咁運都可以</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n3）唔識爆: 有冇人試過用媽媽喺超市買生果嗰隻保鮮袋(非密實袋)？ 我諗應該會容易啲爆？ 但係都係嗰句， 就算唔易爆都好， 佢哋身邊周圍都係水彈， 就好似你細細個落咗波波池一樣， 仲要呢啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">水彈係一踩就爆， 一係就踩落去踩波車仆街</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4）輿論: 大家都擔心會俾人屈係腐蝕性液體， 但係我哋用嘅係保鮮袋， 我覺得由佢點講都冇所謂， 即使佢係話有害嘅不明液體， 一定唔夠其他攻擊物品咁強輿論，加上大家有 laser gun一事加持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，火又出咗，水攻又唔見血<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Btw, 得個講字係冇用, 希望見到有工廠妹/仔會一齊試，現場整完大量， 利用物資鏈運上前線， 再畀前線決定用唔用</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有冇 brainstorm？？？<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔用舊招， 只不過係想加啲新嘢試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964d8efabeda8a41ff2768ffabfe2df9c21a7292","tid":1607795,"uid":65072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"07e88a4a52c125539f98f9c3353c615aa36e1d12","tid":1607795,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.tybook.com.tw/upload/product/upfiles/201405/12/mark_1399909380_69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tybook.com.tw%2Fupload%2Fproduct%2Fupfiles%2F201405%2F12%2Fmark_1399909380_69.jpg&h=8a3c52d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經過文具店，買包氣球<br />\n到現場，搵個公廁<br />\n入水 <br />\n入咩水，可自行發揮<br />\n(影響視嘢顏料 / 能發出氣味為佳)<br />\n完成後，綁好，俾前線<br />\n<br />\n最好可以厚身少少，下面呢種太薄，未送上前易爆<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.junluan.com/program/mall/attachd/image/20190505/20190505005610_34463.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.junluan.com%2Fprogram%2Fmall%2Fattachd%2Fimage%2F20190505%2F20190505005610_34463.jpg&h=9511b6d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住做咩？ 自由發揮啦 <br />\n<img src=\"https://image.bokus.com/images/9781631409738_200x_angry-birds-comics-game-play\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.bokus.com%2Fimages%2F9781631409738_200x_angry-birds-comics-game-play&h=aa445244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:20:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1607402/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1607402/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n［水魔法］有一樣物資各位絲打都有，易入手又難洗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">就係你嘅粉底！！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n顏料貴 連埋水袋好易比狗周<br />\n唔知會唔會多人帶 <br />\n仲要細細枝 好快冇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果個個女仔都帶枝粉底落街就唔怕冇啦</span><br />\n<br />\n痴過粉底落衫既都知 係有幾撚難洗<br />\n唔啱色唔好用過期嘅粉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比人搜都唔怕啊 化妝犯法啊？<br />\n<br />\n拎枝冇用唇膏搽吓嘴仔 又得姐<br />\n齊齊整巫婆湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbab08fa5ffe2d92156a6f13e7bcbad795d482ee","tid":1607795,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/8bdaQvD.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n請大家發揮下創意<br />\n可能來自大家嘅廚房"},{"pid":"fcbc112a148b4a9b72f417b6b3a5e919f5f042fe","tid":1607795,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:24:07.000Z","msg":"男義士仲簡單<br />\n搵個汽球套住條J<br />\n然後小解......<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80941e8e5fb0e7ad63e119ca07cb7e3a9ce733d6","tid":1607795,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:26:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1603280/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1603280/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n點解唔開發新技能用水，對popo傷害好大<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n見上一個po咁多人支持， 睇完下面啲留言，做啲歸納先<br />\n1）加咩都得， 大家創意無限我喺度講都講唔曬<br />\n2）可樂加萬樂珠<br />\n3）可攻擊(濕，笠，臭)，可防禦(跌)<br />\n4）濕膠袋自帶跣既效果<br />\n5）水攻係辛苦死佢地，無孔不入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解決技術性問題<br />\n1）射程: 我哋依家有大彈弓, 但係其實就算掉得唔遠都唔怕, <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>佢地前面成地都係不明液體包括油，梘同埋爆咗嘅膠袋, 跣都跣死</strong></span>，最梗要夠多<br />\n<br />\n2）水:依家打地區戰，水喉水供應多咗， 不過都會有運上前線嘅問題， <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>可能要用黃白藍膠袋或者街市車嗰啲先運到大量， 但係回歸返原始方法， 用人鏈逐隻逐隻保鮮袋水彈咁運都可以</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n3）唔識爆: 有冇人試過用媽媽喺超市買生果嗰隻保鮮袋(非密實袋)？ 我諗應該會容易啲爆？ 但係都係嗰句， 就算唔易爆都好， 佢哋身邊周圍都係水彈， 就好似你細細個落咗波波池一樣， 仲要呢啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">水彈係一踩就爆， 一係就踩落去踩波車仆街</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4）輿論: 大家都擔心會俾人屈係腐蝕性液體， 但係我哋用嘅係保鮮袋， 我覺得由佢點講都冇所謂， 即使佢係話有害嘅不明液體， 一定唔夠其他攻擊物品咁強輿論，加上大家有 laser gun一事加持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，火又出咗，水攻又唔見血<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Btw, 得個講字係冇用, 希望見到有工廠妹/仔會一齊試，現場整完大量， 利用物資鏈運上前線， 再畀前線決定用唔用</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有冇 brainstorm？？？<br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔用舊招， 只不過係想加啲新嘢試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75a0ae0f50428f40ef09a2c838ba52c5ccce35c","tid":1607795,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:28:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=BymrFxr4KeA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBymrFxr4KeA&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdRw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=d06a5575\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=BymrFxr4KeA</a><br />\n<br />\n高級魔法師可以考慮呢種"},{"pid":"74f068b188159daf0beac80a3410fd5926460314","tid":1607795,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:30:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">提示：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3SeKkP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3SeKkP.jpg&h=9be2ab09&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 用防水袋載住，好似唔會咁易爆，就算比人搜到都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 水彈入面放咩唔重要，你鐘意用墨又得，水彩又得，精液都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 用水樽同氣泵唔係多此一舉，試過你就明就咁倒個水彈唔會漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">祝大家10.1玩得開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"17b1b847ada87653126795717afa1805aa499576","tid":1607795,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1xqRfu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1xqRfu.jpg&h=3b5a4bcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻GAME好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}